description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Warren Vache is a supremely accomplished, versatile and rare performer. He has been astounding audiences worldwide for decades with his superb cornet, trumpet and flugelhorn stylings. In this beginners lesson he teaches trumpet basics, such as the parts of the horn, fingering techniques, and note playing.
